        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/75/5411",
        "text": [
          " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْوَصِيَّةِ فَقَالَ \"هِيَ حَقٌّ عَلَى كُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.5411 - Muhammad ibn Al-Fudayl narrated from Abu Al-Sabbah Al-Kinani from Abu Abdullah Imam Al-Sadiq (as), who said: I asked Imam (as) about making a will.\nImam (as) said: \"It is a duty upon every Muslim.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2410,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
